       * @deny (list) Not allowed - document, not a collection.
       * @allow (update) If the user is authenticated and has 'admin' role in the tenant and the document exists.
       * @deny (update) If the user is not authenticated or doesn't have 'admin' role or the document doesn't exist.
       * @allow (delete) If the user is authenticated and has 'admin' role in the tenant and the document exists.
